%F A266083 a(n) = (2*n! + exp(1)*n*(n - 1)*Gamma(n - 1, 1))/2, where Gamma(a, x) is the incomplete gamma function.
%F A266083 a(n + 1) - a(n)*(n + 1) = A000217(n).
