%e A266083 a(4) = 12 + 0 + 12 + 1 + 12 + 2 + 12 + 3 = 54;
%e A266083 a(5) = 54 + 0 + 54 + 1 + 54 + 2 + 54 + 3 + 54 + 4 = 280, etc.
